        "  - Run 'Firefox Nightly Profile Manager', choose 'Scoop-Nightly' then click 'Start Nightly'.",
        "  - Visit 'about:profiles' page in Firefox Nightly to check *DEFAULT* profile.",
        "For details: https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/profile-manager-create-remove-switch-firefox-profiles"
    ],
    "architecture": {
        "64bit": {
            "url": "https://archive.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/nightly/2026/04/2026-04-13-22-08-54-mozilla-central/firefox-151.0a1.en-US.win64.installer.exe#/dl.7z",
            "hash": "sha512:eb826e3242abcf6e3593d12be49e8c0bd79b008fad9b945c316392afde9567534bfd6bed3b37a58836c286831e6f64c1bbf1889d89c1fb75c271c1e09d5f01aa"
        },
        "32bit": {
            "url": "https://archive.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/nightly/2026/04/2026-04-13-22-08-54-mozilla-central/firefox-151.0a1.en-US.win32.installer.exe#/dl.7z",
